<br>
My Question is Has anyone done much test to see what would be the best set up? I was thinking maybe Hammer and Epic till I get aggro built up good then put willsapper in secondary to help hold aggro and more dps but then again I dont know how much better in secondry hand willsapper would accually be over my Red Epic. (im the Guild MA usually) Im pretty sure I wont be seeing any other weapons any time soon other then a Primal Warsword that will be for swaping out reasons only really. So what suggestions do you guys and gals have. Has anyone ran into this before? I hate to bank a really good aggro weapon like the willsapper but on the other hand I want to get the most out of the taunting blow effect I can get.  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
